    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "One-time initializer.\\n\\n- `registry` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 strategy-registry contract; gates authorized callers.\\n- `asset` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 base asset handled by this strategy (e.g. USDC SAC).\\n- `blend_pool` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 Blend V2 pool contract this strategy supplies to.\\n- `reserve_index` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 index of `asset` within the pool's reserve list.\\n- `reward_token` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 BLND emission token contract.\\n- `soroswap_router` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 Soroswap router contract (reward compound).\\n- `soroswap_first_pair` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 pair contract of (swap_path[0], swap_path[1]).\\n- `swap_path` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 must start with `reward_token`, end with `asset`, length \\xe2\\x89\\xa5 2.",
      "name": "initialize",
      "inputs": [
